    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/52168e7099f27cabfa2f7ba3c356b216.webp?t=1730373575\" width=252 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F4stTurt13 is a grey hat, earning a living by completing bug bounties. He hasn’t left his apartment in years. Unexpectedly, he’ll find himself in the midst of conspiracies and on a dangerous path to uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/7b0b4f2599880c2dd102fbee21b2fd9f.avif?t=1730373575\" width=400 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/4ad73629c28690a5cf863b0b5b468056.webp?t=1730373575\" width=315 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> World: In 2032 a large-scale natural disaster ravaged the entire world. It took years for mankind to recover, and two large opposing “countries” were formed in the aftermath. This story is set in the Eastern Alliance of Democracies, comprising Eurasia and Eastern Africa.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> Tech: Due to government policies, the computing power of devices personally owned can’t exceed 1GFLOP. However, an illegal tool, named NeuralNet Jack, was developed and allowed to use the human brain as a “CPU”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> Net: The content available on the net is heavily censored, leading to the creation of an alternative distributed network, called ShadowNet. Its use is considered a crime, but a sizable part of the population (25-30%) access it daily. The main contributors to the Snet infrastructure and code are members of the Neon Knights Collective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/15a6ca94e0c5281e322f8815ab5d08bc.avif?t=1730373575\" width=505 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/4c139745d0adac2c4f85adfc3e6c2e6e.webp?t=1730373575\" width=378 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> Night Hacking is, mostly, an interactive story narrated through chats, files, and websites</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> The hacking process is guided / simple and includes a few “minigames” </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> 7 - 10 hours of content depending  on your reading speed and interest in “side” content </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174540/extras/fa103af2648e5abc95f3e7c24e147a5a.webp?t=1730373575\" width=5 height=9 /></span> There are a few decisions that will impact the ending </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: saving happens only at the end of each level. (Demo progress carries over)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
